    "name": "Hemolysis model validation requirement",
    "description": "The CFD hemolysis model shall be validated against independent experimental measurements of hemolysis in a centrifugal blood pump operating under CPB conditions. Validation evidence must demonstrate that the relative hemolysis index predicted by the model agrees with experimentally measured values within an acceptable tolerance.",
    "requiredVerificationMethod": "experimental-validation"
